{
  "stem": "26728.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hear-- yeah, there were mostly women that I saw the first time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went back 10 days later with some other-- some other people, or a week later, something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by then, they-- the decision had been-- they were no longer carrying the corpses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were bulldozing them and throwing them in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were-- these were civilians from the village-- villages around there, and the British to handle this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were in charge of Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They insisted, the British non-coms, that these bodies be carried either two people or one person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of them were little people, you know, 80 pounds, 60 pounds a dead person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's not very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you couldn't-- they wouldn't let them drag them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My point is they made you-- made you pick them up and physically carry them, as opposed to dragging them by the heel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so that was what was happening the first time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was only there maybe three or four hours and I flew back to Frankfurt or flew on my way back in Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went back, uh, five, six days later with another officer, and I think he was a medical officer, too, because this thing was really desperate.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we got back the second time, he went in and did his business, and I talked to some of these British guys.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that one guy said, 26-- we had 26,000 deaths since you were here before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a sergeant-- a British sergeant, a big-- And he said-- he said I killed one of them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I can't remember what he called the guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, I killed one of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I can remember-- I said, you did?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
